      "message": "feat: improve `ToolsNodes` setup and URL handling logic\n\n- Add `mcp-servers/` to the `.gitignore` file.\n- Introduce `command` and `args` attributes to the `ToolsServer` class with default values.\n- Log the number of `tools_servers` during the `setup` process in `ToolsNodes`.\n- Add detailed logic for handling `stdio-mcp:` URLs in `ToolsNodes` by configuring `command`, `args`, and `transport` as `stdio`.\n\nSigned-off-by: umaru <15875339926@139.com>",
