      "message": "feat: introduce ReAct Agent for structured request handling\n\n- Add detailed requirements for Copilot to carefully understand requests and question unreasonable designs.\n- Replace the base template system with a ReAct Agent template system for a more structured problem-solving methodology.\n- Implement a new `github_tools.py` module to fetch GitHub commit data with validation, error handling, and user grouping based on commits.\n- Introduce pagination support for retrieving GitHub commits efficiently with safety checks.\n- Add a new `ReAct Agent` system prompt template emphasizing reasoning, action steps, security, and safety measures in response handling.\n\nSigned-off-by: umaru <15875339926@139.com>",
